What you need to know:

An accountant by profession, Mutebi also took a short course in interior and design, his artistic hand is inescapable in the house.Clad in a blue suit, Mutebi had opened the gate for us on this Good Friday, but his enforcing-self had ordered us to carry out the chairs for the interview.Mutebi, 51, also believes KCCA can still win the league and Uganda Cup this season.